785
01:08:17,585 --> 01:08:20,401
Kita bicara jutaan dolar.

786
01:08:20,403 --> 01:08:23,704
Itu bisa membeli banyak
permintaan maaf.

787
01:08:23,706 --> 01:08:25,308
